/target
services/*/.spin/

# The repo-root .gitignore blanket-excludes *.json (it was written to keep
# each Python service's real config.json/secrets.json — which contain live
# credentials — out of git). These are synthetic, placeholder-only local-dev
# values (see local-dev/README.md), not real secrets, so re-include them.
!local-dev/config/*.json
